OL,3,CStarmer to face questions from MPs
OL,4,Cafter fresh Trump criticism
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer faces a grilling from
OL,7,FMPs after Donald Trump unleashed fresh
OL,8,Fcriticism of his leadership over the
OL,9,FIran war.
OL,11,FThe Prime Minister will take questions
OL,12,Fin the Commons after the US president
OL,13,Faccused him of making a "big mistake"
OL,14,Fin failing to be "supportive" of
OL,15,FAmerica's military action.
OL,17,FThe Middle East conflict and its
OL,18,Fdomestic impact are likely to dominate
OL,19,Fthe agenda during Prime Minister's
OL,20,FQuestions from noon.
