OL,3,CStarmer to face questions from MPs
OL,4,Cafter fresh Trump criticism
OL,6,FThe president has singled out Britain
OL,7,Ffor criticism over its resistance to
OL,8,Fimmediately agreeing to his calls for
OL,9,Fallies to provide assistance in
OL,10,Freopening the Strait of Hormuz, a key
OL,11,Fglobal shipping route for oil.
OL,13,FWith the war now in a third week, oil
OL,14,Fprices remain above 100 US dollars
OL,15,F(#75) per barrel as a result of
OL,16,FTehran's continued blockade of the
OL,17,Fpassage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
