OL,3,CStarmer to face questions from MPs
OL,4,Cafter fresh Trump criticism
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer insisted on Monday
OL,7,Fthe UK will not be drawn into a "wider
OL,8,Fwar", and said he was working with
OL,9,Fpartners including in Europe on a
OL,10,F"viable collective plan" to free up
OL,11,Fnavigation in the region.
OL,13,FBritain could potentially provide mine-
OL,14,Fhunting drones to the mission rather
OL,15,Fthan a warship, although the Prime
OL,16,FMinister has said no final decisions
OL,17,Fhave been made.
OL,19,FOn Tuesday, Mr Trump said Nato and
OL,20,Fmost other allies have rejected his
OL,21,Fcalls to help secure the strait.
OL,26,@oD@aOUpD@DO]rD@AOUrD@XO]
