OL,3,CStarmer to face questions from MPs
OL,4,Cafter fresh Trump criticism
OL,6,FTory leader Kemi Badenoch has been
OL,7,Fcritical of Sir Keir's response to the
OL,8,Fwar, but nonetheless rejected the
OL,9,Fpresident's attack on him as "wrong".
OL,11,F"It's very childish, this war of words
OL,12,Fand these spats," she told the Press
OL,13,FAssociation on Tuesday.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, Israel said it had killed
OL,16,Ftwo senior Iranian security officials
OL,17,Fin a major blow aimed at further
OL,18,Fweakening the Islamic Republic's
OL,19,Fleadership.
OL,26,@qD@^OUqD@dO]sD@AOUtD@QO]
