OL,3,CStarmer to face questions from MPs
OL,4,Cafter fresh Trump criticism
OL,6,FAli Larijani, secretary of Iran's
OL,7,FSupreme National Security Council, and
OL,8,FGeneral Gholam Reza Soleimani, the
OL,9,Fhead of the Revolutionary Guard's all-
OL,10,Fvolunteer Basij force, were
OL,11,F"eliminated", Israeli defence minister
OL,12,FIsrael Katz said.
OL,14,FTehran has confirmed both killings and
OL,15,Ffired salvos of missiles and drones at
OL,16,Fits Gulf Arab neighbours and Israel on
OL,17,FTuesday.
